CRASH REPORT
------------

On Mac OS, in case of crash, you do agree that the software "ocenaudio" collects and sends diagnostic reports anonymously to "ocenaudio Team". All reports will contain your computer's hardware and software specifications, including information about devices connected to your computer and the versions of the operating system and applications you're using on your computer. None of the information submitted identifies you personally.
You have the option to disable the sending of the diagnostic reports changing the value of the setting "br.com.ocenaudio.application.collect_crash_reports.enabled" to "0".



